.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony, purple, azure, orange
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, polish, indian, nigerian, egyptian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, vegafina, dannemann, davidoff, old-henry
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, mirinda, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
5 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, hamster, goat, mouse

1. the colombian is the person who likes blood-red
2. the polish is the owner of the frog
3. the person drinking juice is the person who likes ebony
4. the indian is the person drinking fanta
5. the person who likes ebony is to the right of the person who likes purple
6. the cain-smoker is the owner of the mouse
7. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes azure
8. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle
9. the nigerian is on the far left
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog
11. the vegafina-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the goat
12. the davidoff-smoker is the person drinking almond-milk
13. the egyptian is the old-henry-smoker
14. the nigerian is to the left or right of the person who likes orange

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   nigerian	|    indian	|     colombian	|    polish	|    egyptian	|
| Color		|    azure	|      orange	|      blood-red	|     purple	|     ebony	|
| Beverage	|     hot-chocolate	|      fanta	|      mirinda	| almond-milk	|     juice	|
| Cigar		|     vegafina	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| davidoff	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     hedgehog	|     goat	|     mouse	|     frog	|     hamster	|
